Forest View is an extension that will elevate your screen ambiance to a wildlife vibe
Search the internet on every new tab with the Forest View.
Additional features include -  settings, clock, todo list and quick access option!

By clicking “Add to Chrome”, I accept and agree to install the Forest View New Tab on the New Tab Chrome extension and setting Chrome™ New Tab search to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The extension will update your search settings and will change your New Tab search services provided by Custom Google Search.
